model_parameters.par_description: Extended length for counting boxes and counting planes
Length x = Total length of sample box in x dimension
Scale factor of sampling boxes to avoid coincident faces (0.995 works well)
Length y = Total length of sample box in y dimension
Length z = Total length of sample box in z dimension
Release plane tolerance - smaller is closer to ideal (0.001 works well)
Number of segments to sample along the x dimension
Plot count of vm molecules in each segment when non-zero
Plot front crossings of vm molecules when non-zero
Time step for each iteration of the simulation
